The paper discusses the management of data in DevOps processes, which involves software engineering practices and database management. Therefore, cs.SE (Software Engineering) and cs.DB (Databases) are the most likely categories. The paper also mentions the use of BigData solutions, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). Finally, the paper discusses new trends in data management, such as DataOps, which falls under cs.CY (Computers and Society).
